 ÿSave Desktopÿ

  This macro saves the current desktop layout. The desktop layout can be
  restored later with the Deskopen macro.

  You will be prompted to enter the desktop file name. If no file
  extension is specified, the file extension .Dst is assumed.

  The following desktop items are saved by this macro:

    - all open file names
    - window sizes and positions
    - window settings
    - cursor states and positions

